reviewText: The girls on the cover aren't in it at all. (I specifically wanted to see more of the back cover girl in blue heels). Incoherent junk pieced together with some amateurish music videos (Suicide Note which is based on Prince's Beautiful Ones, another one about Budweiser, Never Sober (a version of Never Scared). This probably cost about $63.42 total to make. There are naked women but their faces aren't shown for the most part..probably because they didn't know they were being filmed. there is also street footage of women in swimsuits (from Florida?). I would pay at most a quarter to own this and that would be for the picture of the girl on the back cover.
